com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.event

Class DelegatingExecutionEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.event.DelegatingExecutionEventListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecutionEventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AtomicClassLoadingDecorator, AtomicMethodListener, IgnoreFinalFieldsListener, ThreadConfinementListener, ThreadLocalEventListener

    public abstract class DelegatingExecutionEventListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExecutionEventListener
    An ExecutionEventListener that delegates all calls to a nested ExecutionEventListener. Sublasses can override beforeEvent() to supress delegation of method calls.
